com.sociam.android.model

Class ReplyMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sociam.android.model.ReplyMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class ReplyMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    This class is model of a reply of a message. Each reply has to have the message id (parent_id)

    It is used two ways.
    1. it is used when a user open reply dialog and keep input information from the user
    2. When user download the messages, then if a message has reply messages, this class will be instantiate to hold those information.

    Version:
    1
    Author:
    yukki
